{"data":[{"date":"12:56 20/06","title":"Hai con trai c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Pique m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n Colombia","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/hai-con-trai-cua-trung-ve-pique-mac-ao-co-vu-tuyen-colombia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c qu\u00fd t\u1eed c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha, Milan v\u00e0 Sasha, m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">H\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh Milan v\u00e0 Sasha di\u1ec7n \u00e1o m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eb9 Shakira \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n. B\u1ea1n g\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Pique mang qu\u1ed1c t\u1ecbch Colombia v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u01b0 t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u n\u0103m nay. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 d\u1ecbp hi\u1ebfm hoi ca s\u0129 nh\u1ea1c latin khoe \u1ea3nh hai c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c ba v\u00e0 5 tu\u1ed5i. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eafc m\u1eafc: \"Shakira c\u00f3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 khi tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y mai kh\u00f4ng\".<br />\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hai con trai Pique m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Hai con trai Pique m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n Colombia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/cc-1427-1529456960.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Hai con Pique m\u1eb7c \u00e1o c\u1ed5 v\u0169 tuy\u1ec3n Colombia - qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1eb9 Shakira. \u1ea2nh: NS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a hai con trai Pique - Shakira, tuy\u1ec3n Colombia b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 1-2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 m\u1ea5t ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb s\u1edbm sau th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00f4 duy\u00ean v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eafng tay tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n ch\u00e2u \u00c1. Shakira kh\u00f4ng t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Mordovia Arena \u1edf Nga \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp theo d\u00f5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec c\u00f4 \u0111ang trong chuy\u1ebfn l\u01b0u di\u1ec5n \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. Ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ed1c gia b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n g\u1ea7n m\u1ed9t n\u0103m v\u00ec v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 s\u1ee9c kh\u1ecfe c\u1ee7a Shakira.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nN\u1eef ho\u00e0ng nh\u1ea1c latin l\u00e0 fan cu\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00f4n th\u1ec3 thao vua. C\u00f4 kh\u00f4ng \u00edt l\u1ea7n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng Colombia. Shakira c\u0169ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng v\u1edbi b\u00e0i h\u00e1t \"Waka Waka\" t\u1ea1i World Cup 2010. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Nga b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, b\u1ea1n g\u00e1i Pique c\u0169ng tham d\u1ef1 v\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u di\u1ec5n trong bu\u1ed5i l\u1ec5 chia tay \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Colombia l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nSau khi ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh chuy\u1ebfn l\u01b0u di\u1ec5n, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Shakira \u0111\u01b0a hai qu\u00fd t\u1eed t\u1edbi Nga \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 Pique, tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Colombia n\u1ebfu hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt s\u00e2u v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3730","checkdouble":"189031"},{"date":"14:35 20/06","title":"\"H\u1ecda s\u0129 ti\u00ean tri\" World Cup 2018 n\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean MXH v\u00ec ... ph\u00e1n sai","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/20/hoa-si-tien-tri-world-cup-2018-noi-nhat-tren-mxh-vi-phan-sai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1ed9t khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i m\u00e0 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o m\u1eaft xanh, t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ec3 \"th\u00e1nh\" s\u00e1ng t\u00e1c tranh ch\u00e2n dung, th\u00ec d\u00f9 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee1 n\u00e0o, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng kim v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 h\u01a1n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n thua tan n\u00e1t...</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u00e0o l\u01b0u ti\u00ean tri tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi bi\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00f3 l\u1ebd l\u00e0 t\u1eeb 2010 khi World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i Nam Phi v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00fa b\u1ea1ch tu\u1ed9c n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi - Paul. Paul n\u0103m \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 100% k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy v\u1eady, b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 ti\u00ean tri l\u1ed7i l\u1ea1c v\u1edbi x\u00e1c xu\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c cao, v\u1eabn c\u00f2n c\u00f3 c\u00e1c &quot;th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri&quot; kh\u00e1c c\u0169ng n\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m, nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 b\u1edfi si\u00eau n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c &quot;\u0111o\u00e1n to\u00e0n sai&quot; c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfng nh\u1ea5t \u1edf m\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ai kh\u00e1c ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 Vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pele. B\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pele \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao th\u00ec th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7...<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong kh\u00f4ng kh\u00ed s\u00f4i s\u1ee5c c\u1ee7a WC 2018, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y d\u00e2n m\u1ea1ng l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phen x\u00f4n xao truy\u1ec1n tay nhau c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a &quot;th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri World Cup 2018&quot; tr\u00ean MXH. Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c y\u00eau b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 v\u00e0 c\u00f3 t\u00e0i v\u1ebd ch\u00e2n dung, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed7i khi anh ch\u00e0ng vung c\u1ecd v\u1ebd c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, th\u00ec y nh\u01b0 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea3m h\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean MXH V\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3 thua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri World Cup 2018 tr\u00ean MXH V\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed9i n\u00e0o, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00f3 thua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/354050316363903333794507548367927087464448o-15294688824611035461980.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u00e2n dung Messi (Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;N\u00f3i c\u00f3 s\u00e1ch, m\u00e1ch c\u00f3 ch\u1ee9ng&quot;, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u1ecdt m\u1eaft xanh c\u1ee7a Minh \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 si\u00eau sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina Lionel Messi. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ee9c ch\u00e2n dung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Minh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n k\u00e8m d\u00f2ng caption: &quot;Anh em x\u00f4ng l\u00ean!&quot;. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, Messi thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ecfng qu\u1ea3 penalty, Argen ho\u00e0 nh\u1ea1t nho\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u!<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng n\u00f3i n\u1ebfu \u0110\u1ee9c kh\u00f4ng ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c v\u1ebd... B\u1edfi ngay sau \u0111\u00f3, si\u00eau n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a &quot;th\u00e1nh ti\u00ean tri&quot; n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1edbi b\u1ee9c ch\u00e2n dung danh th\u1ee7 Neymar tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Brazil g\u1eb7p Thu\u1ef5 S\u0129. V\u00e0 nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebft, Neymar c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed3i, Brazil - \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean s\u1ed1 1 cho ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch h\u00f2a \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 1 - 1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb s\u1ee9 s\u1edf \u0110\u1ed3ng H\u1ed3.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chan dung Neymar (Anh FB Nguyen Minh Duc)\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n dung Neymar (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/screen-shot-2018-06-20-at-114030-am-1529469656652950322287.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u00e2n dung Neymar (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ee9c v\u1ebd th\u1ee9 3 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng l\u00ean trang c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 y\u00eau m\u1ebfn d\u00e0nh cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c oppa thua 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Thu\u1ef5 \u0110i\u1ec3n gi\u00e0 nua.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chan dung Heung-min Sun (Anh FB Nguyen Minh Duc)\" title=\"Ch\u00e2n dung Heung-min Sun (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/screen-shot-2018-06-20-at-114247-am-15294697897562016298991.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ch\u00e2n dung Heung-min Sun (\u1ea2nh FB Nguy\u1ec5n Minh \u0110\u1ee9c)</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Minh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ebd ch\u00e2n dung l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao Colombia James Rodriguez - c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2014. \u0110\u1ec9nh \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 \u0111en \u0111\u1ee7i l\u00e0 ngay t\u1eeb ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 4, Colombia \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi 10 ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m, c\u00f9ng chi\u1ebfc th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u1ee7a Carlos Sanchez. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Colombia thua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" a