gin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro. H\u1ecd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 khi m\u00e0 c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i theo \u0111u\u1ed5i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m n\u00e0y bao g\u1ed3m Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pjanic \u201c\u0111\u1eaft kh\u00e1ch\u201d tr\u00ean TTCN</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juventus t\u1eeb AS Roma v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 32 tri\u1ec7u Euro m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u0103m 2016, Miralem Pjanic l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng. Anh l\u00e0 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Bianconeri su\u1ed1t 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a Pjanic trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Juventus l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ai s\u00e1nh b\u1eb1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKhi thi\u1ebfu v\u1eafng Pjanic, l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c Juventus b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. L\u1ea5y v\u00ed d\u1ee5 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Real Madrid \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft Champions League m\u00f9a v\u1eeba qua. Tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa \u201cB\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea7m gi\u00e0\u201d kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng d\u01b0\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/7/13/miralem-pjanic-juventus-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic l\u00ean t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Pjanic, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i t\u1ea1i ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 anh. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/juventus-tu-choi-ban-sao-khung-cho-man-city-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-172-187858.html\" target=\"_blank\">Juventus t\u1eebng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i b\u00e1n sao kh\u1ee7ng cho Man City v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</span>. M\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t, c\u1ea3 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Barcelona \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Juventus h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 cao</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o Juventus th\u1eeba hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Miralem Pjanic v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra \u0111i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. T\u1edd Tuttosport m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0a tin Juventus ra gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Pjanic \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro (t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng 70,4 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"tien ve Andres Iniesta chia tay Barca\" title=\"tien ve Andres Iniesta chia tay Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/21/De-Jong-khong-muon-toi-Barca-trong-tuong-lai-gan-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Barca \u0111ang c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay Iniesta</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Barca \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1t m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cao sau khi Andres Iniesta sang Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u201cd\u01b0\u1ee1ng gi\u00e0\u201d. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00fang ra \u0111\u00e3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c\u00e1c ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n Andre Gomes, Denis Suarez \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf khi \u0111\u01b0a h\u1ecd v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00e0 Barca h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang trong \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u00edn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Barca ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh tr\u1ea3 t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u Euro \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Pjanic. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Juventus \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u201cc\u00e2u gi\u1edd\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00fd mu\u1ed1n. H\u1ecd tin n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 Catalonia ch\u1eadm ch\u00e2n, \u0111\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eadp cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng. R\u1ed3i c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Man City hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang c\u00e1ch Pjanic s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng so v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u0169 50 tri\u1ec7u c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Juventus tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-sao-bu-juventus-172-187781.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/23/Monaco-muon-dua-Gonzalo-Higuain-roi-Juventus-hinh-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-co-doi-thu-lon-vu-sao-bu-juventus-172-187781.html\">Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn v\u1ee5 sao b\u1ef1 Juventus</span><br>\r\n<span>Sau Chelsea, t\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Monaco c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Gonzalo Higuain r\u1eddi Juventus, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng C\u00f4ng qu\u1ed1c ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 70 tri\u1ec7u euro cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu-172-188254.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/24/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-juventus-len-ke-hoach-rut-ruot-mu-172-188254.html\">HLV Juventus l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u201cr\u00fat ru\u1ed9t\u201d MU</span><br>\r\n<span>Juventus mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0o H\u00e8 n\u00e0y. HLV Massimiliano Allegri \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3726","checkdouble":"189062"},{"date":"16:38 20/06","title":"CLB HAGL n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau khi T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn l\u1ea1i \"ng\u1ef1a quen \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u0169\"?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/9/6/clb-hagl-noi-gi-sau-khi-tang-tien-lai-ngua-quen-duong-cu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh xung quanh vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn d\u00ednh \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t l\u1ea7n hai v\u00ec h\u00e0nh vi ch\u01a1i x\u1ea5u.</h2><h2>CLB HAGL n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn th\u1ebf n\u00e0o?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a HAGL \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 pha &lsquo;b\u1ecf b\u00f3ng, \u0111\u1ea1p ng\u01b0\u1eddi&rsquo; v\u1edbi ngo\u1ea1i binh Ewonder b\u00ean ph\u00eda ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c C\u0110V \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1ee9c gi\u1eadn. Tuy nhi\u00ean v\u1ecb&nbsp;tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u00f4ng Tr\u1ea7n \u0110\u00ecnh Th\u1ecbnh ch\u1ec9 r\u00fat th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1o T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tang Tien bi phat nang do co hanh vi da xau.\" title=\"T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u0103ng do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ea5u.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/tang-tien-bi-phat-nang-vi-tiep-tuc-choi-tho-bao.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb ph\u1ea1t n\u0103ng do c\u00f3 h\u00e0nh vi \u0111\u00e1 x\u1ea5u.</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau \u00e1n treo gi\u00f2 \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng tho\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t ngu\u1ed9i t\u1eeb ph\u00eda Ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF. C\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb ban k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt VFF \u0111\u01b0a ra \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ea5m thi \u0111\u1ea5u 2 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c n\u00e0y, m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: &ldquo;CLB s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 h\u00ecnh ph\u1ea1t th\u00eam v\u1edbi T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e0o t\u1ea1o khi h\u1ecd ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i th\u00ec m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee1 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00ecm h\u1ecd xu\u1ed1ng, \u0111\u1ea1p h\u1ecd \u0111i. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a CLB l\u00e0 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc. Sau th\u1eddi gian ch\u1ecbu ph\u1ea1t, CLB tin t\u01b0\u1edfng T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, r\u00fat ra cho m\u00ecnh c\u00e1i b\u00e0i h\u1ecdc. R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u00e1c th\u1eeba g\u00e2y ph\u1ea3n c\u1ea3m. CLB s\u1ebd ch\u1ea5p h\u00e0nh \u00e1n ph\u1ea1t c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110VN \u0111\u01b0a ra&quot;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV D\u01b0\u01a1ng Minh Ninh c\u0169ng l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng c\u00e1o bu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e1o. V\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Ewonder th\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 tranh ch\u1ea5p b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i g\u00ec. Nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd khi T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn nh\u1ea3y l\u00ean tranh ch\u1ea5p th\u00ec ch\u00e2n h\u01a1i cao th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ebb v\u00e0ng, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 do l\u1ed7i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u00eam v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, HAGL s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 T\u0103ng Ti\u1ebfn \u1edf hai v\u00f2ng 15 v\u00e0 16. H\u1ecd c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Nguy\u1ec5n V\u0103n H\u1ea1nh b\u1edfi l\u00fd do t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng \u1edf hai v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.</p>\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/6/17/Highlight-Da-Nang-vs-HAGL-.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/17/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/da-nang-21-hagl-chay-ngay-di-truoc-khi-moi-viec-toi-te-hon-168-188780.html\">\u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng 2-1 HAGL: Ch\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n</span><br>\r\nCh\u1ea1y ngay \u0111i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi m\u1ecdi vi\u1ec7c t\u1ed3i t\u1ec7 h\u01a1n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai HAGL \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t v\u1ec1 V-League 2018 n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng trong...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/truong-doan-hagl-viet-tam-thu-sau-chuoi-tran-that-vong-cua-lua-cong-phuong-168-188827.html\">Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n HAGL vi\u1ebft t\u00e2m th\u01b0 sau chu\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a l\u1ee9a C\u00f4ng Ph\u01b0\u1ee3ng</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 HAGL, \u00f4ng Nguy\u1ec5n T\u1ea5n Anh \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m th\u01b0 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i sau chu\u1ed7i 3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ph\u1ed1 N\u00fai t\u1ea1i V-League...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/sau-vong-14-vleague-2018-ha-noi-hagl-dong-loat-nga-ngua-168-188775.html\">Sau v\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018: H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, HAGL \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a</span><br>\r\nV\u00f2ng 14 V-League 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng c\u00fa s\u1ed1c khi H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ecbu thua \u0111\u1ed9i \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC c\u00f2n HAGL ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 ng\u1ef1a tr\u00ean s\u00e2n SHB \u0110\u00e0 N\u1eb5ng. N\u00f3...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3725","checkdouble":"189067"},{"date":"16:54 20/06","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/nguoi-thai-chinh-thuc-len-tieng-ve-kha-nang-cung-viet-nam-dang-cai-world-cup-2034.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u L\u0110B\u0110 Th\u00e1i Lan t\u01b0\u1edbng Somyot Poompanmoung \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra c\u00e2u tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh li\u00ean quan t\u1edbi k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia trong khu v\u1ef1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.</h2><h2>Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y li\u00ean minh M\u1ef9- Canada- Mexico \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2026. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y th\u00fac \u0111\u1ea9y nhi\u1ec1u qu\u1ed1c gia kh\u00e1c ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng tham d\u1ef1 World Cup c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y v\u1edbi t\u01b0 c\u00e1ch n\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034 c\u00f9ng Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/18/viet-nam-thai-lan-len-ke-hoach-dang-cai-world-cup-2034.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Th\u00e1i Lan kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u0103ng cai VCK World Cup 2034</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1eeba qua, \u00f4ng Tengku Abdullah Sultan Ahmad Shah, m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u1ee6y ban \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh FIFA v\u00e0 l\u00e0 C\u1ef1u ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Malaysia cho r\u1eb1ng Th\u00e1i Lan - Vi\u1ec7t Nam - Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin m\u1ed9t chi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 c\u00e1c b\u00ean li\u00ean quan c\u0169ng ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u01b0 World Cup. Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng x\u1ee9 Ch\u00f9a V\u00e0ng, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u00e1i Lan (FAT), Somyot Poompanmoung \u0111\u00e3 thay m\u1eb7t ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o v\u1edbi c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n r\u1eb1ng, th\u00f4ng tin Th\u00e1i Lan mu\u1ed1n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup 2034 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng nh\u1eefng s\u00e2n v\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9ng \u0111\u1ee7 ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n, th\u00eam nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n 5 sao hay c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u01a1 s\u1edf h\u1ea1 t\u1ea7ng giao th\u00f4ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb n\u00e0y c\u0169ng cho bi\u1ebft n\u1ebfu c\u00e1c qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh li\u00ean k\u1ebft t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup th\u00ec hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Malaysia v\u00e0 Indonesia l\u00e0 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1m l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cVi\u1ec7c Th\u00e1i Lan t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c World Cup hay l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1. N\u1ebfu c\u00e1c n\u01b0\u1edbc ASEAN \u0111\u1ed3ng t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Malaysia hay Indonesia l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 quan nh\u1ea5t\u201d, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ee9ng \u0111\u1ea7u FAT nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Trung Qu\u1ed1c c\u0169ng l\u00e0 qu\u1ed1c gia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1y \u0111ua \u0111\u0103ng cai World Cup 2034. V\u1edbi s\u1ef1 gi\u00e0u c\u00f3 v\u1ec1 kinh t\u1ebf c\u00f9ng vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u SV\u0110 l\u1edbn trong n\u01b0\u1edbc, vi\u1ec7c Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t VCK World Cup l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3724","checkdouble":"189070"},{"date":"17:13 20/06","title":"G\u1eb7p \u201ch\u00e0ng l\u1edfm\u201d, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung Qu\u1ed1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/gap-hang-lom-dt-u19-viet-nam-dai-thang-tran-dau-tren-dat-trung-quoc.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 trong chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"G\u1eb7p h\u00e0ng l\u1edfm, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"G\u1eb7p h\u00e0ng l\u1edfm, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1ea1i th\u1eafng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Trung h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/15/Gap-hang-lom,-DT-U19-Viet-Nam-dai-thang-tran-dau-tren-dat-Trung-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm t\u1ea1i Trung Qu\u1ed1c</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t cho gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch U19 \u0110\u00f4ng Nam \u00c1 2018 s\u1ebd kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n k\u00e9o d\u00e0i 10 ng\u00e0y t\u1eeb 15 -25/6/2018 t\u1ea1i Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u, Trung Qu\u1ed1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 v\u00e0o chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y 18/6, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u1ebb c\u1ee7a CLB Meizhou Mexian Techand. Tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n ch\u01a1i l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 trong hi\u1ec7p 1 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 5 l\u1ea7n s\u00fat tung l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u2018qu\u00e2n xanh\u2019.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sang hi\u1ec7p 2, khi nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n h\u1ecd Ho\u00e0ng tung \u0111\u1ed9i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb v\u00e0o s\u00e2n, th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng c\u00e1c ch\u00e0ng trai \u00e1o \u0111\u1ecf v\u1eabn thi \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea5n l\u01b0\u1edbt v\u00e0 ghi th\u00eam m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u1eefa \u00a0\u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 th\u1eafng chung cu\u1ed9c 6-0.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi \u2018qu\u00e2n xanh\u2019 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng song HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0 n\u1eafm b\u1eaft kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 ban hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn t\u00e1i \u0111\u1ea5u Meizhou Mexian Techand c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i B c\u1ee7a CLB Qu\u1ea3ng Ch\u00e2u Evergrande v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 24/6 t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/18/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/vck-u19-chau-a-2018-co-hoi-nao-cho-u19-viet-nam-168-186585.html\">VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam?</span><br>\r\nL\u1ec5 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 t\u1ea1i Jarkata, Indonesia \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0110T Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a hai \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c1 l\u00e0 U19 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, U19 \u00dac. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/15/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/dtqg/u19-viet-nam-cong-bo-danh-sach-sang-trung-quoc-tap-huan-hagl-gop-5-cai-ten-292-188565.html\">U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n, HAGL g\u00f3p 5 c\u00e1i t\u00ean</span><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u0110T U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 danh s\u00e1ch 25 tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd l\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sang Trung Qu\u1ed1c t\u1eadp hu\u1ea5n nh\u1eb1m h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i U19 \u0110N\u00c1 v\u00e0 U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i n\u0103m.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-vck-u19-chau-a-2018-15h00-ngay-185-372-186574.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/17/truc-tiep-boc-tham-vck-u19-chau-a-2018-15h00-ngay-185.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/truc-tiep-boc-tham-vck-u19-chau-a-2018-15h00-ngay-185-372-186574.html\">B\u1ed1c th\u0103m VCK U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018: U19 Vi\u1ec7t Nam r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng kh\u00f3 c\u00f9ng H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, Australia</span><br>\r\nTheo k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ed1c th\u0103m U19 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 2018 v\u1eeba \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c AFC ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ea1i Indonesia, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Ho\u00e0ng Anh Tu\u1ea5n r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ef1c kh\u00f3 v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3723","checkdouble":"189071"},{"date":"17:28 20/06","title":"HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec b\u1ecb mang ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho \u0111i\u1ec3m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/22/hlv-sai-gon-buc-xuc-vi-bi-mang-tieng-duoc-ha-noi-cho-diem.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb v\u1edbi gi\u1edbi truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em t\u1ecf ra th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec b\u1ecb d\u01b0 lu\u1eadn cho r\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 5-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t v\u1edf k\u1ecbch.</h2><h2>HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 14 V-League, \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, CLB S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00e0 12 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m nay ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i. Qu\u1ed1c Ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ghi 1 b\u00e0n trong khi ngo\u1ea1i binh Da Sylva l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa poker b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 5-2 c\u00e1ch bi\u1ec7t.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec b\u1ecb mang ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em b\u1ee9c x\u00fac v\u00ec b\u1ecb mang ti\u1ebfng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i cho \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/22/hoa-ha-noi-fc-hlv-phan-van-tai-em-do-tai-cho-ao-cua-btc.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec b\u1ecb cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i nh\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111i\u1ec3m</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edd \u0111\u1ec3 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng b\u1edfi s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n l\u1ea1i thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebft b\u00e1t v\u00e0 m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 thua \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y, HLV T\u00e0i Em t\u1ecf ra h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn. Nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch AFF Cup 2008 chia s\u1ebb: \u201cH\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng s\u1ee3 b\u1edfi khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb r\u01a1i v\u00e0o th\u1ebf \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f9ng th\u00ec quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Ng\u1ecdc Duy gi\u00fap S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 h\u01a1n. Nh\u1eefng ai \u0111\u00e3 xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y th\u00ec r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ph\u1ee7 nh\u1eadn c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn binh v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t cho bi\u1ebft: \u201cNh\u1eefng ai xem tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u th\u1ea5y ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c ra sao \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau giai \u0111o\u1ea1n l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111i \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u00ec b\u1ecb s\u1ee9t m\u1ebb l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u n\u00ean ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi cu\u1ed9c kh\u1ee7ng ho\u1ea3ng. Anh em trong \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3ng l\u00f2ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i FC v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u00ec S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC m\u1edbi nu\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hy v\u1ecdng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i, S\u00e0i G\u00f2n \u0111ang t\u1ea1m th\u1eddi b\u1ecf xa \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00e9t b\u1ea3ng Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh su\u1ea5t xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam: <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/vleague/lich-thi-dau-25.html\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u, k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, BXH V-League 2018</strong></span><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/du-am-sai-gon-52-ha-noi-su-that-nao-sau-tam-man-nhung-168-188784.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m S\u00e0i G\u00f2n 5-2 H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i: S\u1ef1 th\u1eadt n\u00e0o sau t\u1ea5m m\u00e0n nhung?</span><br>\r\nTrong c\u01a1n m\u01b0a n\u1eb7ng h\u1ea1t t\u1ea1i Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ec1u qua, CLB H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd th\u00fac th\u1ee7 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111ang x\u1ebfp \u00e1p ch\u00f3t tr\u00ean BXH l\u00e0 S\u00e0i G\u00f2n FC. V\u00e0 li\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/18/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/vleague/ha-noi-thua-dam-sai-gon-bat-dau-co-che-xin-cho-291-188777.html\">H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i thua \u0111\u1eadm S\u00e0i G\u00f2n: B\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho?</span><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd c\u1ee7a H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u01a1 ch\u1ebf xin - cho v\u1ed1n v\u1eabn t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i \u1edf V-League, b\u1edfi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nghi v\u1ea5n quanh tr\u1eadn thua...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu-168-188430.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/13/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nam-dinh-co-chien-thang-dau-tay-tren-san-nha-hlv-sai-gon-chi-uoc-1-dieu-168-188430.html\">CLB Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng chung k\u1ebft ng\u01b0\u1ee3c, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n ch\u1ec9 \u01b0\u1edbc 1 \u0111i\u1ec1u</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV S\u00e0i G\u00f2n Phan V\u0103n T\u00e0i Em \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ecf ra \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 cu\u1ed3ng nhi\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a C\u0110V Nam \u0110\u1ecbnh, \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t hi\u1ebfm g\u1eb7p tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3722","checkdouble":"189073"},{"date":"15:11 20/06","title":"3 \u0111\u1ea1i gia ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn v\u00ec Asensio","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/4/26/3-dai-gia-chau-au-dai-chien-vi-asensio.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>MU, PSG v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marco Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Marco Asensio tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh Marco Asensio \u0111\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc. D\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi HLV Zidane, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f3 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m anh c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea9y Gareth Bale l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU, PSG v\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marco Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU, PSG v\u00e0 Chelsea mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marco Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/3-dai-gia-chau-au-dai-chien-vi-asensio.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Asensio \u0111ang ch\u01a1i c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Real</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng qua ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Asensio \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao, ngo\u00e0i ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao \u1edf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a Real Madrid.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarco Asensio c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng sao tr\u1ebb s\u00e1ng gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. HLV Lopetegui ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Real thay Zidane \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 r\u1ea5t cao ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ef1 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Lopetegui Asensio s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean. Gi\u1edbi chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n r\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ph\u1ea9m ch\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1996 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mua Asensio</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh v\u01b0\u1ee3t b\u1eadc c\u1ee7a Asensio gi\u00fap anh l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn tr\u00ean kh\u1eafp ch\u00e2u \u00c2u.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Asensio ghi ban cho Real\" title=\"Asensio ghi ban cho Real\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/26/Diem-tin-bong-da-toi-196-MU-tinh-choi-\u2018tat-tay\u2019-voi-sao-Real-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>MU, Chelsea v\u00e0 PSG mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Asensio\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMU, PSG v\u00e0 Chelsea l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a Marco Asensio r\u1eddi Real Madrid, c\u1ea3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Asensio v\u1edbi Real c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 500 tri\u1ec7u euro, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 chi ra. Tuy nhi\u00ean, MU, PSG v\u00e0 Chelsea tin r\u1eb1ng n\u1ebfu Asensio kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u00e1n n\u1ea3n v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ansensio kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1eb7n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra b\u1edfi trong tay Lopetegui c\u00f2n c\u00f3 Isco hay Gareth Bale.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng, Asensio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn MU, PSG ho\u1eb7c Chelsea \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3721","checkdouble":"189042"},{"date":"14:55 20/06","title":"Ryan Giggs khuy\u00ean Mourinho k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi sao Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/1/ryan-giggs-khuyen-mourinho-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ryan Giggs mu\u1ed1n MU mua Gareth Bale \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Giggs khuuy\u00ean MU mua Bale</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y MU \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Gareth Bale c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. H\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Mourinho ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ryan Giggs mu\u1ed1n MU mua Gareth Bale \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ryan Giggs mu\u1ed1n MU mua Gareth Bale \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/ryan-giggs-khuyen-mourinho-ky-hop-dong-voi-sao-real-madrid.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Giggs khuy\u00ean MU mua Bale</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAnthony Martial \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i, Mourinho \u0111ang nh\u1eafm Bale nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi ra 100 tri\u1ec7u euro nh\u1eb1m thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Los Blanc\u00f3 nh\u1ea3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nRyan Giggs mu\u1ed1n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/mu-gui-them-mot-loi-de-nghi-mua-gareth-bale-172-187655.html\" target=\"_blank\">MU mua Gareth Bale</span> \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tin r\u1eb1ng ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi x\u1ee9 Wales s\u1ebd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 b\u1ed5 sung ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho Man \u0111\u1ecf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a MU v\u00e0 hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t fan h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mua \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gareth Bale. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p, n\u1ebfu Bale t\u1edbi Old Trafford t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 NHM s\u1ebd \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cBale \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u c\u00f9ng Real, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ee5c di\u1ec7n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1ec9 trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc. M.U \u0111ang thi\u1ebfu nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Mourinho n\u00ean t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bale\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Bale l\u00e0 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngay sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2018, Bale kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay Real Madrid: \u201cM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y kh\u00e1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, n\u1ebfu t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ra \u0111i\u201d.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" title=\"guong mat phan cam Gareth Bale\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/1/man-united-chuan-bi-dua-gareth-bale-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Gareth Bale c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real \u1edf H\u00e8 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRyan Giggs tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 M.U c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a Bale tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1edbi Real v\u1eabn c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2022, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Bale \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, n\u1ebfu M.U \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t cao\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTheo Don Balon, t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Bale ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o HLV Julen Lopetegui. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1989 s\u1ebd n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi TBN, n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3720","checkdouble":"189040"},{"date":"15:39 20/06","title":"Santi Cazorla c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi t\u1edbi Jack Wilshere","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/santi-cazorla-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-toi-jack-wilshere.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Santi Cazorla ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00fac c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Arsenal.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jack Wilshere quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Arsenal</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Jack Wilshere v\u1edbi Arsenal ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ebfn H\u00e8 2018, nh\u01b0ng m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng qua. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 s\u1ebd c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Unai Emery tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Santi Cazorla ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Santi Cazorla ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/Santi-Cazorla-phat-bieu-ve-Jack-Wilshere-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wilshere tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay Arsenal</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, Jack Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p v\u1edbi t\u00e2n HLV Emery, sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p n\u00e0y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Theo \u0111\u00f3, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/wilshere-chinh-thuc-roi-arsenal-172-188988.html\" target=\"_blank\">Wilshere \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Arsenal </span>theo d\u1ea1ng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng t\u1ef1 do.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh Wilshere kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \u201cT\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 r\u1eb1ng t\u00f4i s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Arsenal v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ea7u th\u00e1ng 7 t\u1edbi. Sau m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi CLB v\u00e0 cu\u1ed9c n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi HLV Emery, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cArsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gia h\u1ea1n, nh\u01b0ng Emery n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i m\u00f9a t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf. B\u1ea3n th\u00e2n t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean, b\u1edfi v\u1eady t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. Emery l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1eb3ng th\u1eafn, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi Arsenal\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Cazorla c\u00f3 v\u00e0i l\u1eddi mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ebfn Wilshere</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Santi Cazorla ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Jack Wilshere, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u00fac c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh g\u1eb7p nhi\u1ec1u may m\u1eafn sau quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Arsenal.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Santi Cazorla phat bieu ve Wilshere\" title=\"Santi Cazorla ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Wilshere\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/santi-cazorla-co-vai-loi-muon-gui-toi-jack-wilshere.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Santi Cazorla ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Wilshere</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cWilshere l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u1ea5t r\u00f5 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1eddi Arsenal, t\u00f4i t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Wilshere. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nAlexandre Lacazette, Hector Bellerin v\u00e0 Serge Gnabry c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00f4ng tin Wilshere r\u1eddi Arsenal, nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng d\u00e0nh cho\u00a0ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng anh ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t sau khi r\u1eddi Emirates\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3719","checkdouble":"189052"},{"date":"09:43 20/06","title":"S\u00e2n bay qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thay t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/20/san-bay-que-nha-thay-tuong-ngoi-sao-ronaldo.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd s\u00e2n bay Madeira, qu\u00ea h\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh thay b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng anh b\u1eb1ng b\u1ea3n m\u1edbi gi\u1ed1ng nguy\u00ean m\u1eabu h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u1edd Diario de Not\u00edcias Madeira, gia \u0111\u00ecnh Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi xin \u00fd ki\u1ebfn v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 S\u00e1u 15/6, v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a ban qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd s\u00e2n bay Madeira.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"S\u00e2n bay qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thay t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"S\u00e2n bay qu\u00ea nh\u00e0 thay t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/San-bay-que-nha-thay-tuong-ngoi-sao-Ronaldo-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1ecb ch\u00ea v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng kh\u1eafc h\u1ecda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7n th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a anh. \u1ea2nh: AFP.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buc tuong moi duoc nhieu nguoi khen ngoi. Anh: Reuters.\" title=\"B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. \u1ea2nh: Reuters.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/20/35665659-10155671941017957-339-8344-5719-1529409093.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i. \u1ea2nh: Reuters.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng ng\u00f4i sao Ronaldo m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u0169. Ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a ESPN cho bi\u1ebft, danh t\u00ednh c\u1ee7a t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1edbi ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ngay khi ra m\u1eaft, t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi khen b\u1edfi n\u00f3 l\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng t\u1eeb c\u00fa hat-trick c\u1ee7a Ronaldo ghi trong tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo b\u1ecb ch\u00ea l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng kh\u1eafc h\u1ecda \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea7n th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n n\u0103m Qu\u1ea3 B\u00f3ng V\u00e0ng. Nh\u00e0 \u0111i\u00eau kh\u1eafc Emanuel Santos ban \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb7t t\u00ean t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m l\u00e0 &quot;Ronaldo&quot;, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed5i th\u00e0nh &quot;Danh d\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ronaldo&quot; v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 3/2017.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 b\u1ecb ch\u00ea, nh\u00e0 \u0111i\u00eau kh\u1eafc Santos v\u1eabn c\u1ed1 bi\u1ec7n b\u1ea1ch cho b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng Ronaldo c\u0169. \u00d4ng ch\u1ed1ng ch\u1ebf: &quot;Ngay c\u1ea3 Ch\u00faa c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m v\u1eeba l\u00f2ng h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi&quot;, v\u00e0 r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng gi\u1ed1ng th\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd Peticao Publica, v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u1ed9 ph\u1eadn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 th\u00edch b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u0169 h\u01a1n. H\u1ecd d\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u1eedi \u0111\u01a1n ki\u1ebfn ngh\u1ecb \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea5y l\u1ea1i ch\u1ed7 cho t\u00e1c ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Santos.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"3718","checkdouble":"189005"}]}